{"tid":1576672,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"毋忘自殺/被迫害死既義士","createTime":"2019-09-17T10:44:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T11:58:42.000Z","uid":63670,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c39529a7f9970c635493a4381feca131ea455a9a","tid":1576672,"uid":63670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T10:44:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />見到近來咁多離奇無可疑既被自殺案<br />\n我覺得我地唔可以就咁睇完就算<br />\n<br />\n我希望以後每個遊行前可以默哀一分鐘<br />\n證明義士們唔係condom<br />\n再順便提醒埋大家,<br />\n活動之後被濫捕就會有人受到咁<br />\n不人道既對待,所以一定要救人<br />\n<br />\n另外見到個d咁遲先發現既屍體<br />\n真係唔知道佢地生前受到d咩折磨<br />\n強姦,打到骨折,辱罵,精神折磨<br />\n死後屍體仲要不得安寧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n俾人搬黎搬去/掉落海/高空掉落地<br />\n偽造自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地真係唔可以忘記佢地<br />\n<br />\n毋忘831<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n願榮光歸香港，歸義士"},{"pid":"953e3306cf16f7f9fe317ce8abf939f8e61d1fd0","tid":1576672,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T10:45:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yt2HG33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyt2HG33.jpg&h=9fcb0aae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TrPZKfU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTrPZKfU.jpg&h=433e1fe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【922攻略流出】<br />\n907<span style=\"color: gold;\">加強版</span>配合hkmap live <br />\n更「大局」交通測試，彩虹戰衣、影帝、機巴、塞鐵、嶄新突擊RB、私家車傾巢而出，裡應外合 <br />\n+機場員工集體Call Sick <br />\n+雷達站/機場附近新搞作<br />\n+大量中港貨櫃司機加入物資支援！<br />\n<br />\n更多攻略，陸續公布，敬請留意"},{"pid":"55aa36de2d1770662e5fe4191b2e7cf64e8e0778","tid":1576672,"uid":276150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T10:47:39.000Z","msg":"毋忘831<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n願榮光歸香港，歸義士<br />\n血海深仇一定要報！"},{"pid":"9f0bbdd5f192feb24b185e60f3c84dfa941ba912","tid":1576672,"uid":63670,"like":